release.notes:
Record Store Day Black Friday 2022, "RSD Exclusive Release" - 4.500 copies for US market and 11.000 worldwide.

Gold vinyl pressing, issued in gatefold jacket with printed inner sleeves.

Recorded live at the Hammersmith Odeon on November 16th, 1982.

Hype sticker, with catalog number:
Duran Duran Hammersmith '82! 40th Anniversary Edition
Gold 2LP

"Made in Germany" sticker affixed to back cover, upper right on some copies (apparently those packaged for US/non-European [import/export] distribution).

Title on spine:  "Hammersmith '82! LIVE"

Back cover:
℗ 2009 The Copyright In This Sound Recording Is Owned By Parlophone Records Ltd. © 2009 Parlophone Records Ltd., a Warner Music Group Company.
Made In Germany

Labels, inner sleeves:
℗ 2009 Parlophone Records Ltd, a Warner Music Group Company
© 2009 Parlophone Records Ltd, a Warner Music Group Company

Track publishers:
A1 to C2, D2: Gloucester Place Music Ltd./EMI Music Publishing Ltd.
D1: Trigram/RAK Publishing Ltd.

Runouts are etched. In runouts, all Optimal plating symbols may be inverted (e.g., “⊥” vs “T”) and/or mirrored (e.g., “1△” vs “△↾”).
